data.description: Welcome to tranquility, privacy and nature at this private lake home in Gahanna! Step inside, and you're greeted by an atmosphere of warmth and comfort. The interior spaces are thoughtfully designed, with an open floor plan and vaulted ceilings maximizing natural light and encouraging a sense of connection with the outdoors. Upstairs living offers a Jack and Jill bathroom with loft. Finished basement provides a full bathroom, wet bar and murphy bed. Outside, the expansive deck provides the perfect setting for al fresco dining, entertaining guests, or simply soaking up the sun. Intricate landscaping leads you to a private dock extending into waters of the lake, offering endless opportunities for swimming, fishing, boating or simply enjoying the peaceful beauty of nature. New roof 2024.
